'''Fatima Meer'''  (12 Phato 1928 - 12 Hlakola 2010) ebe e le sengwadi sa Afrika Borwa <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/South_Africa</ref>e bile ele  molwantšha kgethologanyo .O belegetšwe Grey Street,Fatima Meer<ref>[[Durban]]</ref>. ke morwedi wa Moosa Meer le Rachel Farrel ,ke ngwana wa bobedi go bana ba seswai . Mmagwe be ele tšhiwana a sena batswadi a dula legae la bana ba ditšhiwana ,tatagwe o belegetšwe Surat <ref>surat</ref>,Gurat. Yo Fatima Meer otšere ngwaga yunibesithing ya WIts a be a ba leloko la la Progressive forum ,o ile a thoma go ruta batho babagolo ka bobeyelo bja sefatanaga bja tatagwe ka ngwaga wa 1940 .Mmereko wa gagwe wa dipolotiki o thomile ge anale mengwaga ye lesome šupa a le sekolong se se phagamego. Fatima Meer e be ele yo mongwe wa diboledi tse kgolo kopanong yeo e bego e swerwe  go lweša mmušo gore o  seke wa tsebiša molao o moswa wa GROUP AREAS ACT .<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Group_Areas_Act</ref> Meer le Dr Goonam<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kesaveloo_Goonam</ref> e be ele basadi ba mathomo go kgethwa goba bagolo ba Natal Indian Congress .O thome  Durban and District Women's League ,pele ga dintwa tsa 1949 tseo di bego di thoma ke makgowa go kgaogantšha makula le bathobaso bao ba bego ba berekišana mmogo go tša dipolotiki bae bitša ANC <ref>[[African National Congress|ANC]]</ref>le Fatima Meer<ref>[[NIC]]</ref>. E  be le sekeretari  le Bertha Mkhize ,mopresidente wa ANC <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/African_National_Congress</ref>WOMEN'S LEAGUE<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/African_National_Congress_Women%27s_League</ref> bjalo ka modulasetulo .E be ele mokgatlo wa mathomo nageng ya rena yeo makula le bathobaso ba bilego ngata e tee .Mokgatlo wo o tsere mathata sebakeng sa basadi ba maAfrika Borwa bao ba bego ba hlorišwa ka lebaka la dipasa ba be ba swariwa ,ya ba ya swara lesolo magareng ga makula go emiša go arogantšhwa ga ma Afrika Borwa le makula.

